data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLER! How does it feel to be treated like the VIP home owner that you are! That's exactly what you will get when you become the owner of this gorgeous bedroom 2.5 bath 4 home in the prestigious  St Claire Community. With access to 6 different community beaches and the Club House available for events and parties, you have all you need for family, friends and even family staycation! Full details can be found at cscia.org. The Roof was replaced one year ago and a new water filtration system for the entire house has been installed. 10 mis from Anne Arundel Community College it is perfect for parents of future students, faculty and staff. Now is your chance to start 2024 in the home of your dreams! CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE OFFERED!
